Haciendo realidad los sueÃ±os. Sport educates and a ball is a powerful tool Would you like to know what we do? We have already donated more than 15,000 balls Sport educates and a ball is a powerful tool Would you like to know what we do? We have already donated more than 15,000 balls After a trip to Brazil together with the NGO â€œRevoluciÃ³n Pelotaâ€ where we donated balls in the Favela â€œComplexo do Alemaoâ€ in Rio de Janeiro, we kept thinking about how to generate a greater impact in more neighborhoods.Â Â  Analyzing the difficulties of most social organizations, we had an idea: start a social enterprise: FC Bola. We created our own brand of balls that is committed to donating a ball for every other ball sold. We have already donated more than 15,000 balls thanks to all those who chose to join this team so that thousands of children without resources can have, many times for the first time in their lives, a new football to play with friends. We grew up playing and we know firsthand how healthy it is to share a passion for sport with friends. We were really lucky as we always had a ball to play with.Â  We are committed to getting involved so that all the boys can enjoy the beautiful game. At FC Bola we sell soccer balls with the commitment that for every Ball sold we donate another one to a boy in a disadvantaged community. This team is committed to the world in which we live. Soccer and the ball are an excuse, what really matters is that children have a place of contention. If we want to dream of a better future, we need a more involved and committed society where those with more resources choose to help to those who do not have the same possibilities. Playing is a right for all children. Sport educates and a ball is a powerful tool for social development. Playing, kids spend less time in the street and more in the field where they learn to work as a team, to share and to make an effort among many values â€‹â€‹that last for a lifetime.Â  To make sure that the balls always reach the feet of the right kids, we are linked with NGOs, schools, clubs and non profits recognized for their supportive and honest work. At FC Bola we like to call them â€œGame Distributorsâ€. From your company, school, club or any type of public or private organization you can join this team so that thousands of children can have a football to play . A Ball is an excellent gift for clients, employees, strategic partners, special guests at events or social responsibility campaigns. May the proposal always be to play together!Â  The donation complement makes our ball much more than a product; it transforms it into part of a history, a mission and a social movement. By joining Bola you become part of a dream: We Want everybody to have a ball to play with.Â  If you are on the same side of the field and think like us, you belong to the vast minority that wants to help. There are different realities, but the passion is the same everywhere. We already work with several large, medium, small companies and government organizations. Yours can also join!
